    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The double-VANOS system is in excellent working order, ensuring a linear power band and crisp throttle response. Power is channeled through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the M-variable differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and a thorough inspection of the rear subframe reinforcement points. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from refreshed bushings and an upgraded suspension setup that maintains factory geometry while enhancing damping. While the paint shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this a prime candidate for those seeking a pure, analog performance machine.",
